  </data>
  <data name="FreOverlay_Card2Description.Text" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>Kawsaq chaymanta ñawpaq agente hunt'akunata qhaway, chaymanta llamk'anaykiman kutiripuy waranqa kama. Qhaway imakunata rurachkan chaymanta ñawpaq llamk'aykunaman kutiy mana chinkachispa.</value>
    <comment>In this context, "agent" refers to an AI agent (e.g. Copilot, Claude, Gemini), not a human agent or representative.</comment>
  </data>
